Author: fishonthesun
Text: Hey with rapid weight loss it tends to come off places that are less in need of fat. So places with organs are gonna keep the fat at first. But if the weight stays off it will slowly redistribute itself to be more proportionate. You may be bloated from water retention or gas. I know if I'm barely eating I get gassy as hell and my stomach hurts
